<div class="strleft">

    	
        
    
		<h1>Vajpayee was unhappy over Gujarat riots handling, reveals ex-R&AW chief AS Dulat</h1>
         <div class="strtitlealias">In an exclusive interview with Karan Thapar on India Today TV, Dulat 
said Vajpayee admitted Gujarat was a mistake. "You could see the sadness
 in his (Vajpayee's) eyes," Dulat said.</div>
        
	
<div class="strstrap" style="width:65%; float:left;">



			<span><a href="http://indiatoday.intoday.in/author/IndiaToday.in/1.html">IndiaToday.in</a></span>
&nbsp;New Delhi,&nbsp;July 2, 2015&nbsp;| UPDATED&nbsp;23:50 IST
 </div>   
   

  
 <div style="width:35%; float:right">
